heading: Stockades Dungeon Guide
content: Stockades a long dungeon that features the . The monster families and layout make this dungeon a bit of a slog, so don't count on running it multiple times. Grab your Renown and head to the next one instead. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
